139
00:20:31,272 --> 00:20:36,475
Back then, what the Lord did physically by Himself, He now does spiritually in the Church every day.

140
00:20:36,475 --> 00:20:48,806
The Church is the spiritual Temple of God, because it can rightly be called a house of prayer, where the Church continuously offers pure prayers to God, saying with the Psalmist, "Let my prayer be set before You like incense (Psalm 140).

